# needed), verify a single sender email (Senders, Domains & Dedicated IPs ->
# Senders -> Add a sender — no domain ownership needed, just click the
# confirmation email they send that address), then create an API key under
# SMTP & API -> API Keys.
BREVO_API_KEY=""
# Must exactly match the email address you verified as a sender.
BREVO_FROM=""
